WEBVTT

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:35.400
to try to understand what some of us call
the "school-to-prison pipeline."

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:38.696
When you look at a picture like this,

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:41.280
of young people who are in my study ...

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:44.856
you might see trouble.

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:49.056
I mean one of the boys
has a bottle of liquor in his hand,

00:00:49.080 --> 00:00:51.216
he's 14 years old

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:52.760
and it's a school day.

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.936
Other people, when they see this picture,

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.976
might see gangs,

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.096
thugs, delinquents --